{"word":"περιβάλλω","slug":"περιβάλλω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>περιβάλλω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:περί\">περί</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:βάλλω\">βάλλω</a></el>] ‘cover around’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of surrounding <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> earthworks: <b>cast up, erect <a href='B:490 19:43'>Lk 19:43</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of covering <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> an article of clothing: of the action, <b>put on <a href='B:470 6:31'>Mt 6:31</a>; <a href='B:480 14:51'>Mk 14:51</a>; <a href='B:490 12:27'>Lk 12:27</a>; <a href='B:500 19:2'>J 19:2</a>; <a href='B:510 12:8'>Ac 12:8</a>; <a href='B:730 19:8'>Rv 19:8</a>.</b> Of the state of one who has put <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> on: <el>περιβέβλημαί</el> (<el>τι</el>) <b>wear <a href='B:480 16:5'>Mk 16:5</a>; <a href='B:730 7:9'>Rv 7:9</a>, <a href='B:730 7:13'>13</a>; <a href='B:730 11:3'>11:3</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:περιαστράπτω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:περιβαλοῦ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}